-- China Sports Official Pledges Athletes Won't Give Fake Ages, Daily Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-29T00:43:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/china-sports-official-pledges-athletes-won-t-give-fake-ages-daily-reports.html

          
          
             China will ensure that there is no
faking of ages by athletes participating in the Youth Olympic
Games in Singapore, the China Daily cited Cai Zhenhua, the head
of the delegation to the games and vice president of the State
General Administration of Sport, as saying.  
 The Singapore competition, which will be held from Aug. 14
to 26, is restricted to athletes between ages 14 and 18, the
report said.  
          
          


  


        